[% WRAPPER h2_section id = "summary"  title = "TL;DR Summary"  %]

<p>
I, Shlomi Fish (a.k.a <a href="[% base_path %]me/rindolf/">"Rindolf"</a>),
am hereby offering to relicense all the current public content that is hosted
in <a href="https://github.com/shlomif/shlomi-fish-homepage">the site's main
repository</a> and its child repositories (e.g <a
href="https://github.com/shlomif/shlomi-fish-homepage/blob/d8f9c9059ec44eb3df8df6158a91f8175bb23e5d/bin/gen-docbook-make-helpers.pl#L149-L152">the
ones in these lines</a>), and is not too private or personal, under <a
href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">CC-BY-4.0-or-later</a>, on
the condition that I receive at least 10 million <a
href="https://www.xe.com/currency/eur-euro">Euro (EUR)</a> to my <a href="[%
base_path %]meta/donate/">PayPal</a> and/or bank account and/or
<a href="https://www.patreon.com/shlomif">my Patreon account</a>.
</p>

<p>
In addition, if I receive at least 100 million Euro, I will make the
texts and the franchises themselves
under an aggregate <a href="#public_domain_license">public-domain / "copyfree" license</a>.
</p>

<p>
I wish to set my intellectual children free to be reused and sublicensed, like
any individual, corporation, or any other organisation pleases.  However, I
wish to have the financial freedom to survive for the foreseeable future. I do
not care if I get the money as many small donations, or as one large donation
by a single rich benefactor, or as something in between.
</p>

